Inline text formatting

To make text bold use double asterisks or double underscore  To make text italic, use single asterisks or single underscore
To make text superscript, use caret
To make text subscript, use tilde
To mark text as inline code, use backticks
To mark text strikethrough, use double tilde

Insert line breaks with backslash or double space

Lists

Ordered lists (for sublists double indent):

  1. Item 1
  2. Item 2
  3. Item 3
    1. Item 3a
      1. Item 3ai
    2. Item 3b
  4. Item 4

Unordered lists (*, +, -):

  • Item 1
  • Item 2
    • Item 2.1
      • Item 2.1.1
  • Item 3

Tasks list: - [] unchecked item - [x] checked item
